        },
        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2019-08-02 16:52:39.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\n> Patch Set 2:\n> \n> Hi. Few things here. \n> Please make sure you read https://wiki.onap.org/pages/viewpage.action?pageId=68540543 for the steps on how to make a release. There are no verify and merge jobs added that i can see. Please add them in ci-management. \n> Given this, the release file did nothing. \n> Please also DO NOT overwrite Jenkins failures...\n\nI would like to echo Jessica here.\n\nDO NOT OVERWRITE JENKINS failures. ESPECIALLY on jobs that are coming from global-jjb. You're doing so is a guarantee that the actual release (since that's what you're trying to do) _will_ fail. If jenkins gives you a -1 there's a _very_ good reason for it.",
